AddressInfo.Title: Walmart Supercenter
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Once your EV is plugged in, your car will tell the charger the maximum power it can accept. This will determine the power level into which you'll be placed and the associated per-minute cost for your entire session. $1 plus $0.89/min at 125kW or more, $0.58/min between 125kW and 75kW, $0.21/min at 75kW or less. Pass+ pricing: $0.60/min at 125kW or more, $0.42/min between 125kW and 75kW, $0.15/min at 75kW or less. 40 cents per minute additional if car not moved ten minutes after session ends. See https://www.electrifyamerica.com/pricing for details.
